# Just dont


## You must disable safeboot from the bios
## You then install the drivers from the displaylink-debian repo on github
## Update the xorg conf
`sudo gedit /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/20-displaylink.conf`
And insert:
```
Section "Device"
    Identifier  "DisplayLink"
    Driver      "modesetting"
    Option      "PageFlip" "false"
EndSection

```
